data.description: Single level 3 bedroom 1 3/4 bath home with nice floor plan,  2 car garage with entry directly into the house, deck off dining room, large fenced back yard.  Peak view of Morro Rock from living room and master bedroom.  Elderly couple purchased this home 1997 and it looks pretty much the same but will need some updating of appliances, carpet, paint inside and out and other upgrades.   Home is clean and in good order and you would be able to move in and do improvements as time permits if that was your choice. Entry, kitchen, dining room, hall, master bedroom all have hardwood floors, 2 bedrooms have carpet and bathrooms have vinyl flooring.  Property was sealed and tented/fumigated on 12-14-23 and also Subterranean Termite application was completed to the soil for a total of $4867.00 by Brezden Pest Control.   As Is Sale, seller will not do any repairs.
